data.description: Welcome to 2175 Rolling Hills in the desirable Tuscany subdivision located just 2.5 miles from I-275!  This cozy condo offers 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a private entry for the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Enjoy the comforts of a well-maintained, almost-new condo that features cathedral ceilings, carpeted flooring, and stainless steel appliances.  Brand new heat pump and hot water heater in 2021 adds to the already low maintenance convenience of condo living.  This community offers the luxury of a clubhouse with a community pool for cooling off and a fitness center to stay active - not to mention the close proximity to the airport, NKU, stadiums and other entertainment spots.
